{"tid":1176214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［清黨］美國運輸部長趙小蘭 被發現違規持有建築公司股票","createTime":"2019-05-29T05:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T09:28:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"952c917b59eb1b0aebdd111e6c37bcc95f7edea9","tid":1176214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"本來簽咗文件答應會清倉<br />\n點知原來仲揸緊<br />\n<br />\nTransportation Secretary Elaine Chao reportedly still holds construction co. stake she pledged to divest<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MufKcon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMufKcon.png&h=37d6e037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\tTransportation Secretary Elaine Chao has held on to her shares of Vulcan Materials, a construction company she promised to divest from more than a year earlier, The Wall Street Journal reports.<br />\n<br />\nChao's shares have risen in value by more than $40,000 since the month she said she would divest them, the Journal reports.<br />\n<br />\nA spokesman for the Transportation Department told the Journal that the agreement she signed was flawed, because it did not account for Vulcan's policy requiring directors' deferred shares to be paid out in shares of company stock.<br />\n<br />\nBut former Office of Government Ethics chief Walter Shaub told the Journal that Chao, whose department oversees U.S. transportation and infrastructure responsibilities, should strive to avoid even the appearance of a potential conflict.<br />\n&quot;For the head of the DOT to have a financial interest in an asphalt company, that is not sending a message to employees of DOT that she is making ethics a priority,&quot; Shaub told the Journal.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/amp/2019/05/28/transportation-secy-chao-reportedly-retained-construction-co-stake-she-pledged-to-divest.html?__twitter_impression=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Famp%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2Ftransportation-secy-chao-reportedly-retained-construction-co-stake-she-pledged-to-divest.html%3F__twitter_impression%3Dtrue&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=763706a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/amp/2019/05/28/transportation-secy-chao-reportedly-retained-construction-co-stake-she-pledged-to-divest.html?__twitter_impression=true</a>"},{"pid":"7b829639267d3759658108481f35c4c7e797d191","tid":1176214,"uid":196924,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"支那種都係差啲.."},{"pid":"fc6b53a8e97cd43fb208eb78a3adb8c74c103371","tid":1176214,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39cc292bff3ed506d31c48f9adbdc561184c384","tid":1176214,"uid":148987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"支那人冇一個係無辜既"},{"pid":"5c700b18dc54dc8e5f5907d219ca27fe4dc253af","tid":1176214,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"睇番香港既囤地波同僭建驊"},{"pid":"db52205e71cfca235b41f55fb997cf0e86cd9453","tid":1176214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c700b18dc54dc8e5f5907d219ca27fe4dc253af","tid":1176214,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:39:24.000Z","msg":"睇番香港既囤地波同僭建驊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"淨係講案情就真係幾輕微<br />\n懷疑想清洗支國人先真"},{"pid":"d1f31cbd2873ca23ff4f6bff48ef8a654b79b1b3","tid":1176214,"uid":5948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:48:01.000Z","msg":"佢好似係台灣人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d581fab32b31be4f5df036ccace746ad5c168971","tid":1176214,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,